tive rates in conjunction with superior service, optimal use of available resources, innovation and cost saving initiatives.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The company aims to maintain and grow on its high profile in the market by:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Maintaining service excellence<\/li><li>Providing superior transport solutions according to each customer\u2019s needs<\/li><li>Treating staff and customers with respect and honesty<\/li><li>Appointing high quality staff (vetted by extensive background checks)<\/li><li>Developing new and innovative ways to safely and cost effectively transport cargo<\/li><li>Offering customers a dedicated, personalised service<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"alignfull wp-block-ugb-count-up ugb-count-up ugb-0f1f87e ugb-countup--v4 ugb-countup--columns-3 ugb-main-block ugb--has-custom-content-width ugb-main-block--inner-full ugb--has-block-background ugb--has-top-separator ugb--has-bottom-separator\"><style>.ugb-0f1f87e .ugb-countup__icon,.ugb-0f1f87e .ugb-countup__counter,.ugb-0f1f87e .ugb-countup__title,.ugb-0f1f87e .ugb-countup__description{text-align:center}.ugb-0f1f87e .ugb-countup__counter{margin-bottom:100px !important;font-family:\"Inter\",Sans-serif !important;font-weight:bold !important;color:#f5f5f5}.ugb-0f1f87e .ugb-countup__title{font-family:\"Inter\",Sans-serif !important;font-weight:bold !important;color:#f5f5f5}.ugb-0f1f87e .ugb-inner-block{text-align:center}.ugb-0f1f87e.ugb-count-up{background-color:#cc191c}.ugb-0f1f87e.ugb-count-up > .ugb-inner-block{max-width:700px !important}.ugb-0f1f87e.ugb-count-up:before{background-color:#cc191c}.ugb-0f1f87e .ugb-top-separator{transform:scale(-1)}.ugb-0f1f87e .ugb-top-separator svg{fill:#ffffff}.ugb-0f1f87e .ugb-top-separator .ugb-separator-wrapper{transform:scaleX(1)}.ugb-0f1f87e .ugb-bottom-separator{transform:scaleX(-1)}.ugb-0f1f87e .ugb-bottom-separator .ugb-separator-wrapper{transform:scaleX(1)}.ugb-0f1f87e .ugb-block-title{font-size:22px !important;font-weight:bold !important;color:#f5f5f5}@